The small has been reconstructed a heart "new of mint", > with a definitive radical correction of cardiopathy, which will give it a normal life, then the neuroendoscopic treatment of hydrocephalus, under the guidance of Dr. Gianluca Piatelli. Arrived in desperate conditions, with black hands, now smiles and touches everything curious and alive again. Her young mother, who left with her, always stayed next to her. He will remain for a few weeks: impossible to return to Palestine. "We were one of the rings of this virtuous chain," continued Roberto Formigari, head of the cardiological team. The child now has a four-room heart and an excellent biventricular function, 100% saturation, without residual defects. From the beginning of the conflict 34 children were followed by the Gaslini Institute: have arrived small patients with burns, mutilation, with painless lesions: more than 40% of the population of Gaza is in the 0-14 range and are they, according to humanitarian organizations, to pay the highest cost of the conflict.&nbsp;
